      "weather": "overcast",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHE'S RAPTUROUS (8) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 29.63 beating STILTON SHINE. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Expected to measure up again. ERUPT (1) was fast into stride from box seven to score two back (30.00) then jumped from the same draw last time but got further back when 4th at this track (30.22). Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to her name from six starts. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. STILTON SHINE (4) turned in a big run last time despite being beaten, finishing second in a Grade 5 behind SHE'S RAPTUROUS in a superb 29.76 and clocking a new PB. In form and looks a leading player again. HURRICANE HALEY (6) is a last start winner and can go on with it.",
